description: Seeks to track the performance of the FTSE Developed All Cap ex North America Index to the extent possible and before fees and expenses. Employs a passively managed, full-replication strategy to provide exposure to the developed global equity markets. U.S. dollar exposure is hedged to the Canadian dollar. Uses efficient, cost-effective index management techniques.
name: Vanguard FTSE Developed All Cap ex North America Index ETF (CAD-hedged)
